         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="MainText">
               <t:label>Main Text</t:label>
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <t:ab>
                     ንዌጥን፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ወትሩፋቲሁ፡ ወገድላቲሁ፡ ለብጹዑ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> ዘተከለለ፡ ስብሐት፡ <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> 
                     ስምዑ፡ ኦአኀዊነ፡ እስመ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ አብ፡ ኮነ፡ ሀገረ፡ ሙላዱ፡ እምሀገረ፡ ዝማ፡
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <t:ab>
                     ወጣኒ፡ ወፋጻሚ፡ ከዳኒ፡ ወረዳኢ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> አሜን።
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Epilogue">
               <t:label>Epilogue</t:label>
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <t:ab>
                   ኦአባ፡ ባርክ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> አምላክ፡ ሰርጐ፡ ዓለም፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ዘኢየኀልቅ።
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
